docs.text: My name is Stuart Christhilf. I am currently a student at Charlotte Latin School. My passions are Engineering and Computer Science. I graduated from fab academy 2023 and am set to graduate high school in 2025. I plan to double major in Electrical Engineering and Computer Science and maybe minor in Mechanical Engineering or Aerospace Engineering once I get to college.
